name: Lunges
details: Challenging your balance is an essential part of a well-rounded exercise routine. Lunges do just that, promoting functional movement.

name: Pushups
details: Drop and give me 20! Pushups are one of the most basic yet effective bodyweight moves you can perform because of the number of muscles.

name: Squats
details: Squats increase lower body and core strength, as well as flexibility in your lower back and hips.

name: dumbbell presses
details: Compound exercises, which utilize multiple joints and muscles, are perfect for busy bees as they work several parts of your body at once.

name: Single-leg deadlifts
details: This is another exercise that challenges your balance. Single-leg deadlifts require stability and leg strength.

name: Abs Workout
details: To do this best ab workout without equipment, get down on the floor on your hands and knees. Balance your body on your toes and palms.

name: Bear Crawl Squat
details: The bear crawl squat works your core, quads, and shoulders, while increasing flexibility in the back of your body. Here's how to do it.
